title.narrative: By 2022, the office has established effective,efficient and transparent financial and administrative support services including anti-fraud systems and culture of fraud detection and prevention.

description.narrative: There was very good performance in assets management, with no asset errors, and 100% implementation of PSB recommendations. An action plan for the improvement of working conditions in all offices was endorsed by the CMT and new premises have been identified for the relocation of the main office in Conakry. Office performance on transaction processing and case submission to GSSC was partially satisfactory on average. At year-end, the budget consumption rate stood at 100%, with no loss of funds on expiry grants. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/12/2019
